My Commute.org

Reading time: 130-165 minutes
Posted here: 15 Apr 2020

https://my.commute.org/#/

A Commute Alternative means going to or from work/college using alternate modes of transportation other than driving alone. Alternate modes include walk, bicycle, transit, shuttle, vanpool, carpool, ferry and/or telework. Green commuting reduces personal carbon footprint and traffic congestion.
